4575.title: Bubble Guppies
4575.description: For Clam Day, the Bubble Guppies decide to throw a party for Clam and invite his cousin Sam. But before they can send Sam an invitation, they need to learn all about how the mail works.

4576.title: Bubble Guppies
4576.description: The Bubble Guppies explore different kinds of ball games as they get ready for their big game of Fishketball! Join Team Guppies to help them practice bouncing, throwing, catching and playing together as a team.

305.title: Bubble Guppies
305.description: Iedereen op de Sjimmie-Sjimmie-eilanden bereidt zich voor op het dansfeest van koningin Zooli. Maar steeds als ze hun liedje voor het feest oefenen, worden ze overspoeld door een grote golf!

11000.title: Bubble Guppies
11000.description: It's going to be the best doghouse EVER! But before Bubble Puppy can move into his new doggy digs, the Bubble Guppies have to build it. Help them build it while discovering all about construction.

11001.title: Bubble Guppies
11001.description: At the Bubble Guppies' restaurant, the group is waiting tables, cooking food,and preparing to serve their most difficult customer yet. But is there anything on the menu that can get the Grumpfish grinning?

6642.title: Bubble Guppies
6642.description: De narren Goby en Gil komen in het koninkrijk Nimmerlach, waar koning Knorhaan bekendmaakt dat hij lachen gaat verbieden als niemand hem voor zonsondergang aan het lachen kan maken! Lukt het de narren om hem op te vrolijken voor het te laat is?

17078.title: Bubble Guppies
17078.description: Are you ready to rock? The Bubble Guppies are taking the stage with their guitars, drums and keyboards. Get ready to crank it up to 10 and learn about everything rock and roll.

17079.title: Bubble Guppies
17079.description: When Oona's friend Avi breaks a bone in his tail, he needs to visit the doctor. The Bubble Guppies aren't too worried - after they learn that it's a doctor's job to make everyone feel better.

12948.title: Bubble Guppies
12948.description: In het oude Griekenland worden ambulanceverplegers Zooli en Gil gebeld door Nonny, die hulp nodig heeft. Ze gaan direct op pad met hun vliegende ambulance! Kunnen ze Nonny helpen voordat de cycloop hen te pakken krijgt?

22872.title: Bubble Guppies
22872.description: The Bubble Guppies are going on a camping trip! Grab your flashlights and gather around the campfire to make s'mores and hear about the spooky legend of Pinkfoot!

22873.title: Bubble Guppies
22873.description: Gil wants to adopt a puppy! But before he can bring the puppy home, the Bubble Guppies must learn how to take care of pets.

19103.title: Bubble Guppies
19103.description: Professor Zooli en haar assistent Gil zijn op zoek naar gorilla's, maar iemand probeert het hen moeilijk te maken. Lukt het hen toch om de zilverrug te vinden?

29246.title: Bubble Guppies
29246.description: Rawrrrrrr! While the Bubble Guppies are digging for dinosaur bones, they learn all about different types of dinosaurs.

29247.title: Bubble Guppies
29247.description: To celebrate Shrimptennial, the Bubble Guppies visit Big Bubble City! Join them in discovering the hustle and bustle of the big city and the Big Bubble Building!

24939.title: Bubble Guppies
24939.description: Ninja's Zooli en Oona krijgen hun eerste missie: de Japanse makaak Moshi naar zijn troep op de top van de Gevaarberg brengen. Maar dat valt niet mee: er komt storm en Moshi is heel ondeugend! Kunnen ze hun missie op tijd volbrengen?

35796.title: Bubble Guppies
35796.description: With an "oink, oink" here and a "moo, moo" there, the Bubble Guppies learn all about farm animals ... and discover that a lot of their favorite foods come from a farm too!

35797.title: Bubble Guppies
35797.description: The play's the thing when the Bubble Guppies go to see a production of 'The Three Little Pigs.' But when one of the actors can't perform, it's up to Deema to put on the costume and take the stage.

31190.title: Bubble Guppies
31190.description: Als de roekeloze hyena Vlekkert de jonge olifant Ollie meeneemt op de savanne, springen opzichters Zooli en Goby in hun truck om hem te redden. Maar als Vlekkert in Ollie in de problemen komen, moeten de guppy's hen helpen.

42245.title: Bubble Guppies
42245.description: The Spring Chicken is about to announce the arrival of spring, but first, she needs a beautiful flower. Help the Bubble Guppies figure out how to plant and care for a flower.

42246.title: Bubble Guppies
42246.description: Glide through the aisles of the supermarket with the Bubble Guppies as they shop for fruits, vegetables and the last box of Bubble Bites for Bubble Puppy!

37876.title: Bubble Guppies
37876.description: Feestkoks Molly en Gil zijn op een missie om het oogstfeest van het dorp te redden en daarvoor moeten ze een gouden tomaat halen op de magische Reuzenboerderij. Maar eerst moeten ze hun kennis over eten bewijzen aan drie wachters!

49152.title: Bubble Guppies
49152.description: Green means GO! The Bubble Guppies are learning about colors while car racing! Help them mix colors, make new shades, and speed across the finish line!

49153.title: Bubble Guppies
49153.description: Learn about different musical instruments as you join the Bubble Guppies' marching band, and help Nonny figure out how to lead the band when there's a duck in the way!

44520.title: Bubble Guppies
44520.description: Kapitein Deemo (Deema) en eerste matroos Gil varen met hun steampunk-onderzeeër naar verschillende oceaanhabitats om zingende vriendschapstelegrammen te bezorgen bij al hun vrienden. Maar onderweg worden ze achternagezeten door een kraken!

55674.title: Bubble Guppies
55674.description: Blast off with the Bubble Guppies - it's time to learn all about the solar system! Help them begin to learn about outer space in this far-out episode.

55675.title: Bubble Guppies
55675.description: Pack a suitcase and hurry to the airport! Help the Bubble Guppies fly an airplane through the sky and over the clouds - just be sure to keep an eye out for airplane pirates!

51236.title: Bubble Guppies
51236.description: In Feestdagenland is er voor elke feestdag een stad. Tenminste, tot piraat Myra de toverstaf van Tovenaar Zeebaars gebruikt om elke stad in een piratenstad te veranderen! Kunnen Molly en Gil alle steden van Feestdagenland weer terugveranderen?

62232.title: Bubble Guppies
62232.description: A friendly squirrel gives Nonny an acorn that will someday grow into a tree! Join the Bubble Guppies in learning all about trees -the animals that live in them, the fruit that grows on them, and how they can help them.

62233.title: Bubble Guppies
62233.description: Ahoy, mateys! The Bubble Guppies are going on a pirate adventure! Gil and Molly meet a friendly pirate with a problem - he can't find his pirate treasure! So with a treasure map in hand Gil and Molly and all their Guppy friends set sail to find where X marks the spot!

57759.title: Bubble Guppies
57759.description: Gil en Bubble Puppy doen mee aan de Wintersport-hondpetitie, een competitie voor sporters en hun honden! Kunnen ze voorkomen dat de regerend kampioenen Sneeuwster en zijn hond Meneer Husky het goud winnen door vals te spelen?

68230.title: Bubble Guppies
68230.description: Meet Monty - the loneliest (and only-est) rhinoceros in the zoo. He needs a friend, and Gil and the Bubble Guppies are determined to help while learning all about habitats at the zoo!

68231.title: Bubble Guppies
68231.description: Once upon a time, Molly and Gil went up a hill to fetch a pail of water. But when a mean Witch, played by Wanda Sykes, turns Bubble Puppy into a frog, Molly and Gil enlist the help of some famous fairytale friends to undo her mean green spell.

64017.title: Bubble Guppies
64017.description: Als de bazige cyborg de Bug alle robots in Robotopolis hackt en dwingt 'de Robot' te dansen, moeten robottechnicus Molly en Robotpuppy hem tegenhouden voor het te laat is!
